I know this time of year can be pretty hard and emotional for many, including myself. Acknowledging and allowing all the emotions that come up to be felt, processed and worked through instead of ignored or dismissed is key. Thoroughly communicate. Honor your boundaries. Take personal time. Prioritize your spiritual health and energy. Release any emotional ties to the choices or words of others. Cherish all the little moments and find joy in all the little things. We all have friends and family who love us. Reach out and check in with each other. You are never alone. 

Sending so much love from our fam to you and yours. ❤️

We are SO PUMPED to make our third headliner announcement of 2023: @nickygenesis 🔥

Nicky Genesis is a Las Vegas based DJ/Producer raised in San Diego, CA. Driven and self taught, she has been DJing for over 15 years up and down the west coast and eventually expanding her shows to a world wide audience. She released her first track on Simplify Recordings in 2011. Since then, Nicky has continued to release tracks on labels such as Night Bass, No Definition, Pinnacle Collective, Glo, Heavy Artillery, Build it, and Bohdi Collective, to name a few. For years she hosted her own radio show on Di.fm radio and has played on diverse stages from countless clubs & festivals all
around the world. 🌎

Nicky has her own unique and beautifuly hitting sound ranging from deep, groovy & soulful, to pulsing bass driven house music and beyond. Her energy and performances take listeners on a journey and leave them with an experience. With multiple channels of growing support across the industry, the future shows to be very promising for this transcending producer. 🔊

We can’t wait to see what she has in store for us at BYL 2023!! 💜 ⁣

What I love most about music is that is is a force that connects us all. The energy we can feel simultaneously that makes us want to smile, cheer, move our bodies. To feel, to release, to flow, to cry, to scream, to wiggle. Whatever it is you’re feeling, you can embrace that or release it on a dance floor. We can communicate with each other without speaking when we listen and dance to music together. We meet on an astral plane where time doesn’t matter. You can lose yourself and find yourself.
